            	&nbsp;
            	<p><strong><i class="fa fa-comments" aria-hidden="true"></i> We welcome feedback. Please contact us <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/contact" data-wpel-link="internal">here</a>.</strong></p>	
																	<div class="post-info"><i class="fa fa-folder-open-o"></i> <span class="thecategory"><a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/budget/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Budget</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/environment/climate-change/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Climate Change</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/congress/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Congress</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/criminal-justice/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Criminal Justice</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/drug-policy/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Drug Policy</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/environment/ecology/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Ecology</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/economics/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Economics</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/education/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Education</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/politics/elections/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Elections</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/environment/energy/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Energy</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/politics/finance-lobbying/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Finance, Lobbying</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/environment/food-agriculture/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Food, Agriculture</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/gun-violence/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Gun Violence</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/health-care/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Health Care</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/housing/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Housing</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/immigration/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Immigration</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/infrastructure-government/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Infrastructure</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/internet/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Internet</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/municipal/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Municipal</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/society/public-health/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Public Health</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tip-sheets/reporting/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Reporting</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/government/security-military/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Security, Military</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tip-sheets/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Tip sheets</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/environment/transportation/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Transportation</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/studies/international/foreign-policy/" rel="category tag" data-wpel-link="internal">U.S. Foreign Policy</a></span> <i class="fa fa-tags"></i> <span class="thecategory">
							<a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/goldsmith2020/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">2020 Goldsmith finalists</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/center-for-public-integrity/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">Center for Public Integrity</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/model-legislation/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">model legislation</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/news-collaboration/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">news collaboration</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/the-arizona-republic/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">The Arizona Republic</a>, <a href="https://journalistsresource.org/tag/usa-today/" rel="tag" data-wpel-link="internal">USA Today</a></span></div>
